# NPM Scripts

| Script | Command | Purpose |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `dev` | `astro dev` | Local dev server |
| `build` | `astro build` | Production build (output in `dist/`) |
| `preview` | `astro preview` | Preview production build locally |

## Deployment

Deployment is automatic via Cloudflare Workers on push to `main`. Do NOT add manual deploy steps to npm scripts.

## Dependencies

- `wrangler` is a devDependency for Cloudflare config schema and local preview — do NOT remove it
- Do NOT add `@astrojs/cloudflare` — this is a static site
